angular

1.component-html,css,ts(type script)-root component,app component=>Building block=>html view componentnu ullond

2.module-root module,app module

3.data binding

            3.1->one way binding-data flow in 1 direction
                1.component to view
                    1.string interpolation/interpolation -syntax:{{expression}}
                    2.property binding-syntax:[binding-target]="binding source"
                2.from view to component
                    1.event binding-syntax:(event)="function call"
                    2.event binding using $event-syntax:(event)="function-call($event)"
                    3.template referring variable-syntax:#variable_name
            3.2->two way binding-2 direction(ngModel-formsmodule)syntax:[(ngModel)]="variable_name"
                if ngModel in form tag then set name property

4.angular routing(oro web page-num path set cheyyan)

5.Dependency injection-in constructor(constructor anu oru classil adyam execuite akunnath..
                                       .athanu constructoril kodukkunnath)-
                       syntax:object:dependent_class_name
                    
6.Angular Services-   syntax:ng g s service_name   [src=>app=>srvice folder create akki]

7.ngSubmit

8.Angular forms

  8.1-template driven angular  forms

  8.2-model Driven angular forms

      8.2.1-Reactive forms-for validating a web page-ReactiveFormsModule(3rd party library import cheyyanm)-ethu pagene aano cheyyamdey aaa pagenu 3 part venm(Form group,Form arrray,FormControl name)

9.Angular Directives-DOM manipulate cheyyan
   
     9.1-component directives-component use cheyth dom il change aakka
     9.2-Structural directives-adding or deleting component ,syntax:*
             
             9.2.1-ngIf-syntax:*ngIf="condition" -ethelum condition vech change venel(add or delete)
             9.2.2- ngFor-syntax:*ngFor=""

10.Local storage
    10.1.setItem-to store values
    10.2.getItem-to call a value
    10.3removeItem-to remove a item from local storage

11.import HttpclientModule-front end and backend integreate cheyyan
  11.1 inject  Httpclient in data service

12.RXJS(reactive extension of js) -library-async events ayittullath eggane resolve akkunnath egganeyann angularil parayunnath
     12.1 observable- .subscribe()

13.angular pipe-(syntax:expression | pipie operator[:pipe argument])user input cheyyunna kargl transform cheyyan vendi